Let  $A_i$  be the event that number  $i$  appears at position  $i$  or to the left of number  $i$ . i. e.  $(i|A_i )$ . By inclusion-exclusion,
\[
\begin{eqnarray*}
|A_1 \cup A_2 \cup \dots \cup A_6| &=& \sum _i |A_i| - \sum _{i<j} |A_i \cap A_j| + \sum _{i<j<k} |A_i \cap A_j \cap A_k| \\
& &- \sum _{i<j<k<l} |A_i \cap A_j \cap A_k \cap A_l| + \sum _{i<j<k<l<m} |A_i \cap A_j \cap A_k \cap A_l \cap A_m| - |A_1 \cap A_2 \cap A_3 \cap A_4 \cap A_5 \cap A_6| \\
&=& \binom{6}{1} - \binom{5}{2} + \binom{4}{3} - \binom{3}{4} + \binom{2}{5} - \binom{1}{6} \\
&=& 6 - 10 + 4 - 1 + 0 - 1 \\
&=& \fbox{0} 
\end{eqnarray*}
